  "detailed_description": "A sci-fi adventure with shooter and puzzle elements.<br />\r\nIn this game you will plunge into an amazing new world.<br />\r\nThe world of the guardian. A world in which reality has been split apart and then sewn back together again.<br />\r\nShin-kai-\"city\", the first part of a large-scale and fascinating adventure narrating the journey of a mythical creature torn from his world and time and thrown into the whirlpool of events, in the ruined world of post-communism.<br />\r\n1959 in the Soviet Union finds a mysterious object.<br />\r\n2034, Soviet ideology becomes world leading, all countries unite into a single communist union.<br />\r\n2094 an alien signal is received.<br />\r\n2109 year.....<br />\r\n2402 year, huge dirty hall, in the middle of the room, among the scraps and garbage, there is a box and it seems someone is in it....<br />\r\n12 unique, varied levels.<br />\r\nAn interesting and unusual story, which will introduce you to a new, vast universe.<br />\r\nThe gameplay takes 2-4 hours.<br />\r\nFive parts of the game are planned.",
  "about_the_game": "A sci-fi adventure with shooter and puzzle elements.<br />\r\nIn this game you will plunge into an amazing new world.<br />\r\nThe world of the guardian. A world in which reality has been split apart and then sewn back together again.<br />\r\nShin-kai-\"city\", the first part of a large-scale and fascinating adventure narrating the journey of a mythical creature torn from his world and time and thrown into the whirlpool of events, in the ruined world of post-communism.<br />\r\n1959 in the Soviet Union finds a mysterious object.<br />\r\n2034, Soviet ideology becomes world leading, all countries unite into a single communist union.<br />\r\n2094 an alien signal is received.<br />\r\n2109 year.....<br />\r\n2402 year, huge dirty hall, in the middle of the room, among the scraps and garbage, there is a box and it seems someone is in it....<br />\r\n12 unique, varied levels.<br />\r\nAn interesting and unusual story, which will introduce you to a new, vast universe.<br />\r\nThe gameplay takes 2-4 hours.<br />\r\nFive parts of the game are planned.",
